name: Runivers: Cultural and Historical Project
description: A digital library of primary sources for Russian history and culture. Subject categories are listed on the left of the screen. See 'Zhurnal'nyi zal' for such historic journals as Russkii arkhiv, 1863-1917; Put': Organ russkoi religioznoi mysli, 1929-1940; Voprosy filosofii i psikhologii, 1889-1918; and Zhurnal Ministerstva narodnogo prosveshcheniia, 1834-1917. In Russian.
